high_descs: Turn left to walk to the sink.
Pick up the large knife in the sink.
Turn right to walk across the room to the fridge.
Slice the apple inside the fridge.
Turn to face the fridge.
Set the knife down in the fridge.
Turn to face the fridge.
Pick up a slice of apple.
Turn left to walk to the stove.
Set the apple slice in the leftmost pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot with the apple slice in it.
Turn around to walk to the far corner of the room where the table is.
Set the pot with the apple slice down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple to put in a pot to take to the table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right and step forward to face the fridge.
Cut the apple in the fridge into three pieces.
Look down to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Look up to face the fridge.
Pick up the apple piece in the fridge.
Turn left and walk forward to face the stove.
Place the apple piece in the left pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot with an apple piece in it.
Turn left and walk forward and left to face the left end of the table.
Place the pot on the table.
anns.task_desc: To put an apple piece in a pot plus place it on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and face the sink.
Grab the knife from the sink.
Turn around and walk then turn left and face the fridge.
Slice the apple that is in the fridge.
Back up from the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Get closer to the fridge again.
Grab an apple slice from the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the stove.
Place the apple in the pot on the left.
Grab the pot with the apple in it.
Turn around and walk then walk right to the table.
Place the pot on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with an apple slice in it on the table.
